<%- include('partials/head') %><%- include('partials/navbar') %><main class="container py-5"><div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 p-4 p-lg-5"><h1><%= heading %></h1><p class="lead text-secondary"><%= message %></p><% if(currentPath==='/about'){ %><p>PrizeMania began as a 2023 university PHP/MySQL project. This rebuild keeps its simple blue-and-white monthly draw identity while demonstrating modern Express architecture, database transactions, secure sessions and accessible responsive design.</p><p>No real money or banking data is used. New development users receive a simulated wallet balance.</p><p class="small text-secondary">Project archive: <a class="link-secondary" href="/docs/prizemania-original-university-project.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">view the original COS-209 university documentation <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-up-right ms-1" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>.</p><% }else{ %><p>This portfolio project is maintained by Aung Min Khant. For questions, use the project repository contact details. PrizeMania does not operate a real gambling or payment service.</p><% } %><a class="btn btn-primary align-self-start" href="/">Return home</a></div></main><%- include('partials/footer') %>
